交叉分析步骤

  • 1.显著性检验

对单选题使用列联表卡方独立性检验，对多选题使用多元方差分析(MANOVA)来检验两个变量是否存在联系，即在不同用户特征下，多选题各个选项的选择比例是否相同。

  • 2.交叉分析可视化[Barplot]

交叉分析柱状图可视化

ggfun <- function(dat, x.var, f.var,theme){

  x.var <- rlang::sym(quo_name(enquo(x.var)))
  f.var <- rlang::sym(quo_name(enquo(f.var)))
  
  pvalue <- chisq.test(dat[[x.var]],dat[[f.var]])$p.value

  ggp <- 
  ggplot(data=dat,aes(x=!! x.var,fill=!! x.var))+
    geom_bar(aes(y = (..count..)/tapply(..count..,..PANEL..,sum)[..PANEL..])) + 
    geom_text(aes(y = ((..count..)/tapply(..count..,..PANEL..,sum)[..PANEL..]), 
  label = scales::percent((..count..)/tapply(..count..,..PANEL..,sum)[..PANEL..],accuracy = 1L)), stat = "count", vjust = -0.25)+
    facet_wrap(~dat[[f.var]]) + 
    labs(y = "频率",x='',title=x.var,subtitle = paste0('Chisq p value:',round(pvalue,3))) +
    scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent)+
    # scale_fill_manual( values = c( "#a6cdd9", "#d2e4ee", "#b7b079", "#efc750" ) ) +
    theme( strip.text = element_text( size = 12, color = "white", hjust = 0.5 ),
       strip.background = element_rect( fill = "#858585", color = NA ),    
       panel.background = element_rect( fill = "#efefef", color = NA ),
       panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(),
       panel.grid.minor.x = element_blank(),
       panel.grid.minor.y = element_blank(),
       panel.grid.major.y = element_line( color = "#b2b2b2" ),
       panel.spacing.x = unit( 1, "cm" ),
       panel.spacing.y = unit( 0.5, "cm" ),
       legend.position = "none" )+
     cowplot::theme_half_open(12) +
     cowplot::background_grid() +
  theme(
      strip.background = element_blank(),
      strip.text = element_textbox(
      size = 12,
      color = "white", fill = "#5D729D", box.color = "#4A618C",
      halign = 0.5, linetype = 1, r = unit(5, "pt"), width = unit(1, "npc"),
      padding = margin(2, 0, 1, 0), margin = margin(3, 3, 3, 3)
    )
  )+
       theme(text = element_text(family = "STXihei"))+
       theme(axis.text.x=element_blank())+
       scale_fill_tableau(theme)+
       theme(legend.position = "bottom" )

  return(ggp)
}
(p5_45 <- ggfun(dat = data, x.var = `5、您的消费习惯是？`, f.var =`45、您的性别：`,theme = 'Red-Blue-Brown'))

(p6_47 <- ggfun(dat = data, x.var = `6、您的实际消费情况和计划符合吗？`, f.var =`47、您的年级：`,theme = 'Purple-Pink-Gray'))

GGplot插入图片(cowplot)

横向图片

p <- ggplot(iris, aes(x = Sepal.Length, fill = Species)) + geom_density(alpha = 0.7)
p2 <- ggdraw() + draw_image("http://jeroen.github.io/images/tiger.svg", scale = 0.9)
plot_grid(p, p2, labels = "AUTO")

x轴刻度图片

# create the data
set.seed(123)
myd <- expand.grid('cat' = LETTERS[1:5], 'cond'= c(F,T), 'phase' = c("Interphase", "Prophase", "Metaphase", "Anaphase", "Telophase"))
myd$value <- floor((rnorm(nrow(myd)))*100)
myd$value[myd$value < 0] <- 0

# make the barplot
pbar <- ggplot(myd) +
  geom_bar(aes(y = value, x = phase, fill = cat), stat="identity", position='dodge') +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 224), expand = c(0, 0)) +
  theme_minimal(14) +
  theme(axis.ticks.length = unit(0, "in"))
# make the image strip
pimage <- axis_canvas(pbar, axis = 'x') + 
  #both for local file or website file
  draw_image("http://www.microbehunter.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2009/lily_interphase.jpg", x = 0.5, scale = 0.9) +
  draw_image("http://www.microbehunter.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2009/lily_prophase.jpg", x = 1.5, scale = 0.9) +
  draw_image("http://www.microbehunter.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2009/lily_metaphase2.jpg", x = 2.5, scale = 0.9) +
  draw_image("http://www.microbehunter.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2009/lily_anaphase2.jpg", x = 3.5, scale = 0.9) +
  draw_image("http://www.microbehunter.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2009/lily_telophase.jpg", x = 4.5, scale = 0.9)

# insert the image strip into the bar plot and draw  
ggdraw(insert_xaxis_grob(pbar, pimage, position = "bottom"))
